<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Account Approved!</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #0e2f52; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; background-color: #f8f9fa; }
        .email-container { background: #ffffff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.1); }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ed956, #0987c9); color: white; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; }
        .header p { margin: 10px 0 0 0; opacity: 0.9; font-size: 16px; }
        .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
        .content p { color: #5a6c7d; margin: 0 0 20px 0; }
        .content p strong { color: #0e2f52; }
        .success-card { background: #dcfce7; border-radius: 12px; padding: 25px; margin: 25px 0; border-left: 4px solid #7ed956; text-align: center; }
        .success-icon { width: 60px; height: 60px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7ed956, #22c55e); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 15px; }
        .success-icon svg { width: 30px; height: 30px; fill: white; }
        .success-text { color: #166534; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
        .features { margin: 30px 0; }
        .feature { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .feature-icon { width: 40px; height: 40px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin-right: 15px; flex-shrink: 0; color: white; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; }
        .feature-text h3 { margin: 0 0 5px 0; color: #0e2f52; font-size: 16px; }
        .feature-text p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; }
        .btn-container { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0987c9, #7ed956); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 16px 40px; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(9, 135, 201, 0.3); }
        .support-box { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin-top: 25px; text-align: center; }
        .support-box h4 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; color: #0e2f52; font-size: 14px; }
        .support-box p { margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #5a6c7d; }
        .support-box a { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
        .support-box a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 25px 30px; background: #f8f9fa; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
        .footer p { margin: 0; color: #5a6c7d; font-size: 14px; }
        .footer .brand { color: #0987c9; font-weight: 600; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You're Approved!</h1>
            <p>Welcome to Volunteens</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= organizationName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>Great news! Your organization account has been approved and is now active. You can start using Volunteens to connect with motivated young volunteers.</p>

            <div class="success-card">
                <div class="success-icon">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M9 16.17L4.83 12l-1.42 1.41L9 19 21 7l-1.41-1.41z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div class="success-text">Your account is ready!</div>
            </div>

            <div class="features">
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">1</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Create Events</h3>
                        <p>Post volunteer opportunities and define shifts that work for your schedule.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">2</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Manage Volunteers</h3>
                        <p>Review signups, confirm participants, and assign them to specific shifts.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature">
                    <div class="feature-icon">3</div>
                    <div class="feature-text">
                        <h3>Track & Pay</h3>
                        <p>Record attendance and receive automated invoices for volunteer compensation.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="btn-container">
                <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="btn">Go to Dashboard</a>
            </div>

            <div class="support-box">
                <h4>Need Help?</h4>
                <p>Our B2B support team is here to assist you with any questions.<br>
                Contact us at <a href="mailto:<%= supportEmail %>"><%= supportEmail %></a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p><span class="brand">Volunteens</span> - Connecting young volunteers with opportunities</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
